They have up to three hits between them (just like Volleyball) to control the ball and bounce it back off the net. When they miss, you score. 3) Did we mention that there are no boundaries? Once a point starts, players can move or hit the ball anywhere. 2 on 2 play similar to Volleyball No Boundaries or Sides Each team has 3 hits to spike the ball into the net Points are scored when ball hits the ground or a team can't return the ball to the net within 3 attempts First team to 21 wins
